But again, we're going to flash the survey here in a little bit, or the chat with us

00:14:17.080 --> 00:14:18.080
as well.

00:14:18.080 --> 00:14:21.640
That will help kind of book a call and you can we can talk a little bit about your team,

00:14:21.640 --> 00:14:25.919
your needs and get you a kind of a really customized Posit Connect instance for your

00:14:25.919 --> 00:14:26.919
group.

